    "last_edit_date" : 1743508221,
    "creation_date" : 1712734580,
    "answer_id" : 78302791,
    "question_id" : 18779183,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Three things to be done as below :</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>Check all three in Settings &gt; Maven &gt; Importing &gt; Automatically download sources, documentation and annotations.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Update your <code>settings.xml</code> in <code>.m2/repository</code> ( doesn't matter if you already have your settings anywhere else, copy that to default repository i.e .m2/repository.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Run <code>mvn dependency:sources</code> ( it always uses settings placed at .m2/repository )</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 6115775,
      "reputation" : 35173,
      "user_id" : 4770877,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/p5TXj.png?s=256",
