  "title" : "Can not download sources with Intellij Idea community 12.1.4 and maven 3.0.5",
  "body" : "<p>I click \"download sources and documentation\" in Intellij Idea Community Edition 12.1.4 and get error that sources can not be downloaded.\nBut when I try:</p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn dependency:sources\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>All sources are downloaded.</p>\n\n<p>What is the problem?</p>\n\n<p><strong>P.S.</strong> I have checked that Idea use the same maven that use in console. There are not any \"off line\" mode buttons triggered in Idea.</p>\n"
